<p></p>
<a href="/recipes/food/views/Chocolate-Cake-with-Vanilla-Buttercream-109040"><h3>Chocolate Cake with Vanilla Buttercream</h3></a>

<br /><br />
<p><span class="dropCapFirst">W</span>
hat could improve a classic birthday cake? How about a stack of mini cupcakes on top. To make decorating easier, place the cake on a rotating lazy Susan before frosting it. </p> 

